}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to the Eurostar, you can bookreturn ticketsfor less than \\u00a3100 if you travel before the Olympics start on July 26.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4084797887552106e-19, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Evans-Fisk, head of digital and engagement ateurochange, said: \\\"Paris is known as one of the most expensive cities in Europe and travelling to and from it usually does not come cheaply either.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"digital and engagement ateurochange\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the most expensive cities\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So if you can save some money getting there, you should seize that opportunity.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some money\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"that opportunity\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In July through to September when the Olympics come to the French capital, travel, accommodation and public transport costs will almost skyrocket.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8635297678511039, \"rank\": 0.15764754994744112, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"accommodation\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport costs\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"M\\u00e9tro tickets are set to double in price, with a book of 10 increasing from \\u20ac16.90 to \\u20ac32.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"M\\u00e9tro tickets\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"price\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"a book\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The average hotel price is set toincrease by 92%andair fares by 21%.\\\"\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The average hotel price\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"toincrease\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"92%andair fares\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"21%\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura explained that now was also the best time to visit Paris ahead of the crowds descending on the city over the next few months.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"