 [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing experience\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"my advice\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Over50% of hotels across the whole of Franceare fully booked over this period, and the number is increasing daily.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Over50%\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"Franceare\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"this period\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to experience Paris without the crowds and price hikes, now is definitely the best time to visit.\\\"\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1761, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"price hikes\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"the best time\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For travellers visiting Paris over the next few months, whether it's for the Olympics or just before the event, Laura shares her budgeting tips to help you save your cash in the city.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"travellers\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few months\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"her budgeting tips\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"your cash\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get your travel money in advance Laura said: \\\"Typically, the EUR rate only moves very slightly over any given month.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.045163820066184e-40, \"text\": \"EUR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your travel money\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"any given month\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even when the exchange rate differs marginally when buying larger amounts, it can soon add up, so it's worth keeping a close eye on the exchange rate before you head to Paris.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528898522993526e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the exchange rate\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"larger amounts\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"a close eye\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the exchange rate\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would always recommend buying your euros before you get to the airport or Eurostar train station, as the exchange rates tend to be far higher than when you buy in advance, in branch or online.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4084797887552106e-19, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your euros\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"the airport\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"the exchange rates\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"branch\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, Monday through to Thursday is the best time to buy your euros, as these are the least busy days for transfers, so you might see a little less fluctuation in the mid-market rate.\\\"\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"the best time\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"your euros\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"the least busy days\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2629}, {\"ngram\": \"transfers\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"a little less fluctuation\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the mid-market rate\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Use public transport, and buy your tickets in bulk Laura said: \\\"It's a great idea to get hold of a weekly or monthly pass if you are planning to use public transport on your trip.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.8161382359496102, \"rank\": 0.22526147737514549, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"your tickets\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"a great idea\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"a weekly or monthly pass\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"your trip\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will help you save quite a bit of cash.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite a bit\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"cash\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although prices are set to increase for the Olympics, if you are going to be using public transport regularly, it will still be more cost-effective to buy in bulk.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prices\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2955}, {\"n